high_descs: Turn around and head to the grey table on your right.
Grab the turner on the table.
Head over to the pot on the left.
Put the turner in the pot on the left.
Pick up the pot in front of you.
Head over to the counter on your left.
Put the pot down on the counter
anns.task_desc: Move a pot with a turner to another counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk until you are even with the small white table to your right and then turn and walk to it.
Pick up the spatula that's near the edge of the table.
Adjust your position slightly to the left so you are still facing the table.
Put the spatula in the silver pan with a handle.
Pick up the pan with the spatula.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Put the pan on the counter right under the orange gift bag.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a spatula in it on the counter.

high_descs: You will rotate circle for three quarters and on the right pick up an tomato.
You will cross the room to the small white table, pick up the tool.
You walk around stop, twist and circle back to the same table for the bowl
You drop the item in the bowl.
The bowl is picked up as to hold the tool in it.
You have to turn to the left.
You walk to the left and cross the room to the counter. And to slide the bowl forward.
anns.task_desc: It make an few tools come together as the robot knows they belong near the kitchen sink.
